<item>
            <title>[LU-18004] import_select_connection() is using CONNECTION_MAX instead of CONNECTION_MIN</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18004</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Patch v2_15_61-238-g94d05d0737 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17379&quot; title=&quot;try MGS NIDs more quickly at initial mount&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-17379&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-17379&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, is using CONNECTION_SWITCH_MAX when trying to shrink the connection timeout instead of CONNECTION_SWITCH_MIN.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
 &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;/* make it quick at first round */&lt;/span&gt;
 &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (timeout &amp;gt; CONNECTION_SWITCH_MIN)
                 at_reset(at, CONNECTION_SWITCH_MAX);&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
